# Exponential Idle Game Puzzle('s) Solver

This will be a "cheater" system for exponential idle game puzzles.

For now it has a simple interface for doing the arrow puzzle.
There will be a possibility that it will be expanded to include the other puzzles as well.

## Usage

Clone the repo and open the html page in your browser. You can then use the interface to solve the arrow puzzle.

